item.title: Prayer bpn6320 in Namibia
item.description: #EVERURO ##(HEALING) Edina Lyoge yilyo everuro Lyange, Hompa gwange, ano edivoroko Koge o mutji gwange. Pepi Nove eli ehuguvaro lyange, eharo lyoko Koge ukwao. Nkenda Zoge kwange everuro lyange nepameko lyange mouzuni ou nomomauzuni ogo ngaga wiza ko. Yousili, Ove, Mugavigwanayinye, Mudivigwanayinye, Mukonentu gwanayinye. (Source category: Rukwangali: EVERURO) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 6320)
